            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1467213477,
            "creation_date": 1467213477,
            "body": "<p>You can use Apache commons-math3 to generate random numbers.\nIt has got lots of useful methods for this.\nSee interface \"RandomGenerator\" and its implementing classes.<\/p>\n",
